                                                          EXPERIMENT NO -1
                                                         Analysis of CS Amplifier

 Aim: 
    To analyze a common-source (CS) amplifier with specifications of 180 nm technology, 1.8 V supply voltage, and a power budget of 50 μW through DC analysis, transient analysis, and AC analysis, and to extract parameters such as DC operating point, DC analysis, gain, bandwidth, and power.

APPARATUS:
	NMOS Transistor (CMOSN-nmso4)
	Voltage Source ( VG - 0.9V, VDD – 1.8v)
	Resistors (1K OHM)
	Ground
	CONNECTING wires

THEORY:
